    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"let the weight go\" ... it feels like there's no way to do that without it being permanent. i look at his side of the bed and it's just... it feels wrong for me to still be here, you know? like i'm just occupying space that doesn't belong to me anymore. sometimes i feel like i'm just waiting for something to happen so i can finally be at peace.",
